Package hu.zza.clim

Provides the fundamental classes for building a Menu. Building it is quite easy with MenuBuilder which is a top-level builder. There are other builders for components, like MenuStructureBuilder and ParameterMatcherBuilder. ClimOption provides a common interface for various enums used to setup Menu at building.
Since:
0.1
